column5: Come on out and check it out. Cheap admission, free parking. Drop by and say hello. Niagara Outdoor Show
There will be a number of area OFNers with booths at the show. Denisk of Fishin Niagara, Fishmasters. I'll be there with Ugliboys baits.  Stop in and say hello.
If your a walleye guy or girl then you will like the assortment of blades beads and complete harnesses on site.  Looking forward to it
